:"致力于分享自己学习笔记的萌新博主","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/AienH","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"qq":{"icon":"/svg/qq.svg","link":"https://user.qzone.qq.com/2313406889"}}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"linux之crontab定时任务","uid":"6a675661b44d95ca224ff64405dd19fd","slug":"linux之crontab定时任务","date":"2023-05-15T14:48:27.000Z","updated":"2023-05-17T13:13:24.347Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/linux之crontab定时任务.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/medias/1682924542965.jpg","text":"Linux crontab 命令Linux crontab 是用来定期执行程序的命令。 当安装完成操作系统之后，默认便会启动此任务调度命令。 crond 命令每分钟会定期检查是否有要执行的工作，如果有要执行的工作便会自动执行该工作。 注意：新创建的 cron 任务，不会马上执行，...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"3.6k","symbolsTime":"3 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"linux","slug":"linux","count":6,"path":"api/categories/linux.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"命令","slug":"命令","count":1,"path":"api/tags/命令.json"}],"author":{"name":"ienAの博客","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://aienh.github.io/images/20230401000222.jpg","link":"/","description":"致力于分享自己学习笔记的萌新博主","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/AienH","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"qq":{"icon":"/svg/qq.svg","link":"https://user.qzone.qq.com/2313406889"}}}}},"next_post":{"title":"ztncui私有化zerotier来创建moon","uid":"c1f784f1241b8ade5ed5cc99958c6ee6","slug":"ztncui私有化zerotier来创建moon","date":"2023-05-04T15:33:25.000Z","updated":"2023-05-20T13:00:43.450Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/ztncui私有化zerotier来创建moon.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/medias/1668057372218.jpeg","text":"简介zerotier one是众多内网穿透工具平衡性最好的。方便速度快部署简单的比他贵的多，速度比他快比他便宜的部署麻烦，比他便宜部署容易的使用体验又不好。 不过zerotier one的虚拟网络是由官方控制器控制的，虚拟内网被别人控制总感觉不会不舒服。好在zerotier是开源...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"7.5k","symbolsTime":"7 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"orangepi","slug":"orangepi","count":4,"path":"api/categories/orangepi.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"zerotier","slug":"zerotier","count":1,"path":"api/tags/zerotier.json"},{"name":"moon","slug":"moon","count":1,"path":"api/tags/moon.json"},{"name":"内网穿透","slug":"内网穿透","count":2,"path":"api/tags/内网穿透.json"}],"author":{"name":"ienAの博客","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://aienh.github.io/images/20230401000222.jpg","link":"/","description":"致力于分享自己学习笔记的萌新博主","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/AienH","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"qq":{"icon":"/svg/qq.svg","link":"https://user.qzone.qq.com/2313406889"}}}}}}